<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.8.6">
<l>eṇṭi caikaḷu mēḻu lakamum vāṅkip poṉvayiṟ ṟilpeytu</l>
<l>paṇṭō rālilaip paḷḷi koṇṭavaṉ pāṉma tikkiṭart tīrttava</l>
<l>ṉoṇṭi ṟalavu ṇaṉu rattukir vaitta</l>
<l>vaṉoḷḷe yiṟṟoṭu</l>
<l>tiṇṭi ṟalari yāya vaṉtiru vēṅka ṭamaṭai neñcamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[My] heart, take refuge at Tiruvēṅkaṭam of the one who became</l>
<l rend="indent">a powerful, strong lion with bright teeth,</l>
<l>The one who thrust his claws into the chest of the bright, strong demon,</l>
<l>The one who ended the suffering of the milky moon,</l>
<l rend="indent">who, having taken up the eight directions and seven worlds,</l>
<l>Having poured [them] into his golden stomach,</l>
<l rend="indent">previously slept on an banyan leaf.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
